text:
1. Grasp the parallel bars with both hands.
2. Lift your body off the ground by pushing down on the bars.
3. Keep your body straight and parallel to the ground.
4. Swing your legs forward and backward to maintain balance.
5. Move your arms in a controlled manner to shift your body weight.
6. Lower your body back down to the starting position by bending your arms.
7. Repeat the steps to continue performing parallel bars.
